Package: StatBayes
Title: Interactive Bayesian Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2026-07-02
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Manuel",
           family = "Spinola",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "mspinola10@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7839-1908"))
Description: An interactive and didactic Shiny application for applied Bayesian
    analysis using brms. Covers prior distributions, Bayesian linear and
    generalized regression, generalized additive models, mixed models, MCMC
    diagnostics, and model comparison (LOO, WAIC). Part of the StatSuite
    ecosystem, ICOMVIS, Universidad Nacional, Costa Rica.
